5.1 No Commercial Use is authorized without a valid paid commercial license
from Licensor.

5.2 Standard commercial license fees are as follows ("Schedule A"):

| Tier | Installs Covered | Fee |
|------|-----------------|-----|
| Solo Commercial | 1 Install | USD $199 per year |
| Team | Up to 5 Installs | USD $499 per year |
| Business | Up to 25 Installs | USD $1,499 per year |
| Enterprise | Unlimited | Custom — contact Support@GoZippy.com |

Annual licenses are renewed each year. Installs exceeding a tier's limit require
upgrade to the next tier before the excess Installs may be used commercially.
All fees are per-calendar-year unless a separate written agreement specifies
otherwise.

5.3 Unlicensed Commercial Use penalty: Any Commercial Use discovered without a
valid paid license is subject to a retroactive fee of **USD $1,000 per Install**
for the full period of unlicensed use, plus the cost of bringing the deployment
into compliance under the applicable tier going forward. This penalty rate is
not the standard purchase price — it applies only to unlicensed use discovered
through audit, self-report, or enforcement.

5.4 Any Commercial Use without payment of the applicable fee is unauthorized
and constitutes a material breach of this License.

5.5 If You discover that You have been making Commercial Use without a valid
license, You have thirty (30) days from the date of discovery to obtain the
required license before Licensor may pursue enforcement remedies solely based
on that prior unauthorized use — provided You: (a) promptly pay all fees
accrued from the start of Commercial Use at the standard tier rate (not the
penalty rate), (b) cease unauthorized use immediately, and (c) self-report to
Licensor at Support@GoZippy.com in writing. The reduced-rate self-reporting
grace period is available once per entity.

5.6 Payment of a fee grants only the limited Commercial Use rights stated in
this License and does not transfer ownership or convert this License into an
open source or permissive license.

5.7 Licensor may offer alternative enterprise, volume, OEM, partner, reseller,
or custom commercial terms in a separate written agreement. Contact
Support@GoZippy.com for enterprise licensing inquiries.

5.8 No Managed Service Use. Regardless of whether a commercial license fee has
